OL,3,C'I was in Number 10 and a few months
OL,4,Clater I was in a prison van': Former MP
OL,6,FFormer Labour MP Mike Amesbury says he
OL,7,Fwants to serve as a lesson to others
OL,8,Fafter losing his home and his career
OL,9,Fwhen he punched a constituent during a
OL,10,Fnight out almost a year ago.
OL,12,FAmesbury, who was the MP for Runcorn
OL,13,Fand Helsby told ITV Granada Reports he
OL,14,Fhas applied for more than 30 jobs but
OL,15,Fis still not in full-time employment.
OL,17,FThe 55-year-old pleaded guilty in
OL,18,FJanuary to assaulting his constituent
OL,19,FPaul Fellows, 45, after a row in the
OL,20,Fstreet in Frodsham, Cheshire on 26
OL,21,FOctober 2024.
