OL,3,C'I was in Number 10 and a few months
OL,4,Clater I was in a prison van': Former MP
OL,6,FHe was given a 10-week prison term and
OL,7,Fspent three days behind bars before it
OL,8,Fwas reduced to a suspended sentence
OL,9,Ffollowing an appeal and he has since
OL,10,Fresigned from Parliament.
OL,12,F"I have said it repeatedly, I am
OL,13,Fprofoundly sorry. I shouldn't have
OL,14,Fdone what I did and I have owned it,"
OL,15,Fhe said.
OL,17,F"I'm still in the community. The
OL,18,Ffamily home is now sold because
OL,19,Fcollectively as a family we couldn't
OL,20,Fafford it.
