OL,3,C'I was in Number 10 and a few months
OL,4,Clater I was in a prison van': Former MP
OL,6,F"It's had a strain in terms of my
OL,7,Fpersonal life and of course there was
OL,8,Fthe victim Mr Fellows."
OL,10,FFootage showed Amesbury punching Mr
OL,11,FFellows to the head, knocking him to
OL,12,Fthe ground, then following him on to
OL,13,Fthe road and starting to punch him
OL,14,Fagain, at least five times.
OL,16,FAmesbury said: "I remember being in
OL,17,FNumber 10 on three different occasions
OL,18,Fsince the General Election not long
OL,19,Fago, and then I was in a prison van a
OL,20,Ffew months later. It's been a journey."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
