OL,3,C'I was in Number 10 and a few months
OL,4,Clater I was in a prison van': Former MP
OL,6,FSpeaking of life since the incident,
OL,7,Fhe said he had struggled to find a
OL,8,Fjob, and even at times an interview.
OL,10,F"Since my conviction out of the 30
OL,11,Fplus applications I have got through
OL,12,Fto a selection centre with another 30
OL,13,Fcandidates for one job and I wasn't
OL,14,Fsuccessful. The other organisations I
OL,15,Fhaven't even got an interview," he
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,F"Some were positively disabled
OL,19,Femployers. I do have a disability.
