OL,6,F"Even when the box was ticked it was
OL,7,Fsupposed to be a guaranteed interview
OL,8,Fbut I didn't get an interview. Some of
OL,9,Fthese organisations were charities.
OL,10,FSome were trade unions.
OL,12,F"I'm disappointed for those
OL,13,Forganisations. The charities that
OL,14,Fclaim to be charitable but are far
OL,15,Ffrom charitable. It's probably another
OL,16,Flesson in life. I have had lots of
OL,17,Fthem in the last year."
