OL,3,C'I was in Number 10 and a few months
OL,4,Clater I was in a prison van': Former MP
OL,6,FFormer Conservative councillor and
OL,7,FReform MP Sarah Pochin beat Labour's
OL,8,FKaren Shore in the Cheshire
OL,9,Fconstituency of Runcorn and Helsby by
OL,10,Fonly six votes in the by-election
OL,11,Ffollowing a recount.
OL,13,FAmesbury said he is aware actions may
OL,14,Fnow mean a battle between Labour and
OL,15,FReform UK at the next election after
OL,16,Fhis resignation allowed the party to
OL,17,Fgain a foothold in the North West.
OL,19,F"It opened the door didn't it. It
OL,20,Fopened the door to that opportunity,"
OL,21,Fhe said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
